"
" Sets standard Vim settings for this project.

" Turn on automatic indenting:
set ai sw=4

" If tabs do exist, they should be 4 spaces wide:
set ts=4

" If tabs do exist, expand them to spaces.
set expandtab

" Set the page gutter:
set colorcolumn=80
